  "title": "[ENTRY LEVEL] EVENT AND SALE CREW",
  "description": "<p><strong>🔥 Join Our Events Marketing Team – No Experience Needed! 🔥</strong></p>\n<p>We’re hiring <strong>Brand Ambassadors</strong> to represent top brands at <strong>events, roadshows &amp; campaigns</strong>.<br>\nGet <strong>paid to learn</strong>, <strong>travel</strong>, and <strong>grow your career</strong> in sales &amp; marketing!</p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote and represent brands at exciting events</li>\n  <li>Engage customers &amp; boost sales</li>\n  <li>Work with a supportive, fun team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Get:</strong><br>\n✅ Competitive pay + incentives<br>\n✅ Training &amp; coaching provided<br>\n✅ Fast-track career growth opportunities</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Positive, confident, and eager to learn</li>\n  <li>Min GCE ‘N’/‘O’ Level (or equivalent)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🚀 <strong>Start your journey today – Apply now!</strong></p>",
